{"tid":1068293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大媽300萬人仔買別墅 無屋頂全屋水浸","createTime":"2019-03-19T06:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T23:51:26.000Z","uid":130626,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"07441800e1d56c8009ca2d1bed88afff7be757ca","tid":1068293,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:32:29.000Z","msg":"福建福州一名陳姓女子，早前花300萬人民幣（約357萬港元）購買一幢別墅，近日接到開發商通知可以收樓，不料她發現別墅竟沒有屋頂，導致全屋室內到處水浸，因此拒絕簽收。開發商則解釋，屋頂是「贈送面積」，如果要蓋屋頂的話就算產權面積。<br />\n據了解，贈送面積是許多內地開發商售樓的手法，例如聲稱贈送地下室、窗台、露台等的面積。不過開發商所講的「免費」，其實有的本來是買房者應得；有的是開發商擅自改變規劃，屬於違建的面積，令業主在所有權上得不到法律保障，甚至還可能沒法辦房產證。<br />\n當地媒體報道，陳女購買的別墅位於福州寶龍森鄰龍泉山莊。對於當初買樓時為何沒留意到缺少屋頂，她表示，當時跟別人一起看的是示範單位，因為已經裝修好，無論是外觀還是內部都非常漂亮。<br />\n龍泉山莊的開發商則指，該別墅是按照規劃設計施工的，並且大部分已經驗收通過；在交樓前，他們曾經試圖在屋頂上蓋一個簡易遮雨棚，然而因為中途施工隊的原因擱置了，這也導致陳女的別墅到處都是積水。<br />\n陳女向內地媒體透露，她曾向開發商提出能否自行興建屋頂，惟發展商拒絕交樓前動工。最終發展商承諾願意先行抽走別墅積水，並已提出解決方案，雙方暫時達成共識。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_j01BQ4MTt_ZiDihh5rBIg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/adce9d3f7af0e6b15fdd62d6e20ae4ea\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F_j01BQ4MTt_ZiDihh5rBIg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fadce9d3f7af0e6b15fdd62d6e20ae4ea&h=9a9266bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳女購買的房子位於福州寶龍森鄰龍泉山莊。（電視畫面）<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/polzkA6muy03ZD_.5RKpqg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/84203f7ea43478e01f20703971d00552\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpolzkA6muy03ZD_.5RKpqg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F84203f7ea43478e01f20703971d00552&h=61e0897e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開發商稱屋頂是贈送面積。（電視畫面）"},{"pid":"6f9be0f84d19cbc4bbc9508065cb84f48045afca","tid":1068293,"uid":3765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無言"},{"pid":"175fe0cae41608f12c7abec12747bbbdc9678688","tid":1068293,"uid":33668,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:35:16.000Z","msg":"肥媽教你返大陸買樓"},{"pid":"ad2333a004960196b4f07b0dcb581732957e1a41","tid":1068293,"uid":14361,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:36:39.000Z","msg":"去大灣區置業<br />\n買水浸樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d120974a80daa2813862d2fe3362c4ef07e333","tid":1068293,"uid":122134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"175fe0cae41608f12c7abec12747bbbdc9678688","tid":1068293,"uid":33668,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:35:16.000Z","msg":"肥媽教你返大陸買樓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:39:19.000Z","msg":"記唔記得肥媽個幢係邊<br />\n惠洲?"},{"pid":"38a2dc09b39a3717a26618e87bfaa047ecae47b0","tid":1068293,"uid":196484,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:50:59.000Z","msg":"點都一定好撚過香港 完"},{"pid":"20a289f9e70b53704c7b57c7aca0237e5fe33dc9","tid":1068293,"uid":212493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:54:52.000Z","msg":"要俾錢起屋頂<br />\n提升GDP<br />\n又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c35efe69e3b30ebf9f22c9bcfc805ca5c71a62","tid":1068293,"uid":86723,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:56:25.000Z","msg":"買樓都有DLC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d16e2d2949573591d2d292d62c4e01e7d6b6d6","tid":1068293,"uid":220853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit